  "data": {
    "title": "CallHippo Tips: 7 Best Ways to Boost Sales Calls",
    "excerpt": "Discover proven tips to get the most out of CallHippo's virtual phone system. Close more deals with these best practices for sales teams.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/callhippo-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "CallHippo Tips: 7 Best Ways to Boost Sales Calls",
        "filename": "callhippo-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have tested dozens of cloud phone platforms over the past three years. Most promise the moon and deliver a walkie-talkie with extra steps. CallHippo is the rare tool that actually earns its keep — especially if your team lives and dies by outbound sales calls.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Below, I am sharing seven concrete tips to squeeze every ounce of value from CallHippo. Whether you run a five-person SDR squad or a 200-seat global contact center, these practices will help you connect faster, sell smarter, and keep your pipeline healthy.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Grab Local Numbers in Every Target Market",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is CallHippo's bread and butter, and it works shockingly well.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo offers virtual numbers in 50+ countries. The trick is not just buying a US number and calling London. The trick is buying a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "London local number",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " when you prospect into the UK, a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sydney number",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " for Australia, and so on.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why? People answer local caller IDs at dramatically higher rates than unknown international codes. One SDR team I coached saw their connect rate jump from 12% to 31% after switching to local numbers for three European markets. Same reps, same scripts, same prospects — just a different area code.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Set up country-specific numbers during onboarding. CallHippo lets you provision them in minutes. Label each number clearly in your dashboard so reps always dial from the right one.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-callhippo"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you want a walkthrough, check our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step CallHippo tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. Use the AI Voice Agent for After-Hours Inbound",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://callhippo.com/ai-voice-agent"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One of CallHippo's newer products is the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Voice Agent",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — and it speaks like a real human. I am not exaggerating.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here is where it shines: after-hours inbound calls. Instead of sending callers to a generic voicemail that nobody checks until morning, the AI agent picks up, answers FAQs, captures lead details, and even books meetings on your calendar.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A mid-size SaaS company I work with deployed the AI agent for their APAC traffic (which hits outside US business hours). Within two weeks, they recovered 40+ leads that would have bounced straight to voicemail.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Feed the AI agent your top 20 prospect questions and the correct answers. Update them monthly as your product evolves. The better the training data, the more natural the conversations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. Set Up IVR Like a Pro (Not Like a Bureaucracy)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Interactive Voice Response (IVR) gets a bad rap because most companies build maze-like phone trees that frustrate callers. CallHippo's IVR builder is drag-and-drop simple, which means you can design a flow that actually helps people instead of trapping them.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Best practice:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Keep it to two menu levels maximum.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Say the most common option first (\"Press 1 for Sales\" if 80% of calls are sales).",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Always include an escape hatch to reach a live person.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Record greetings with a real human voice — not a robot.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo supports multi-level IVR, time-based routing, and skills-based assignment. You can route Spanish-speaking callers to bilingual reps automatically, or send enterprise prospects straight to your AE team while SMB leads go to SDRs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Review your IVR analytics every two weeks. If you see callers dropping off at level two, simplify. CallHippo's dashboard shows exactly where people hang up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-callhippo"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to explore more reasons this platform stands out? Read ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "why choose CallHippo",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. Record Every Call — Then Actually Review Them",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call recording is table stakes for any serious phone platform. CallHippo does it automatically, but the real power is in the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "conversation analytics",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " layer on top.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform tags calls, transcribes them, and highlights keywords. You can search for every call where a rep mentioned \"pricing\" or where a prospect said \"competitor.\" This is gold for coaching.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here is my recommended cadence:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Weekly:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Each manager reviews five random calls per rep. Score them on talk-to-listen ratio, objection handling, and next-step clarity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Monthly:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Pull the top 10 highest-converting calls across the team. Use them as training material in your sales meetings.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Quarterly:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Analyze keyword trends. Are prospects asking about a feature you do not market? That is product feedback hiding in your call logs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Turn on call recording for inbound and outbound. Some teams skip inbound recording and miss half the coaching opportunity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. Stack CallHippo With Your CRM for Zero-Data-Entry Workflows",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo integrates natively with Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, Zoho, and more. But I see too many teams leave the integration shallow.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Go beyond basic call logging. Set up these automations:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Auto-log calls",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " as activities in your CRM with duration, outcome, and recording link.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Screen pop:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " When a call comes in, the CRM record should flash on screen so the rep sees deal stage, last email, and notes before saying hello.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Post-call triggers:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " After a call marked \"Interested,\" automatically move the deal to the next stage and fire a follow-up email template.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This removes the manual data entry that kills rep productivity. One team I worked with reclaimed 45 minutes per rep per day just by automating call logging.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-apollo-io"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you use ",
