      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "6. Leverage the Parallel Dialer to Multiply Conversations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your team runs high-volume outbound campaigns, the Parallel Dialer is a game-changer. It dials multiple numbers simultaneously and connects your rep only when a live human answers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The math is simple: instead of spending 30 seconds listening to ringing per prospect, your reps spend that time talking. Over a four-hour outbound block, this can double the number of live conversations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Combine the Parallel Dialer with CallHippo's call scripts feature. Load your pitch directly into the platform so reps can glance at key talking points without switching tabs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "7. Watch the Omnichannel Inbox to Catch Missed Opportunities",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo is not just phone calls anymore. Their Omnichannel Inbox unifies voice, SMS, WhatsApp, and email in a single view. This means your reps never miss a prospect who replies to an SMS follow-up or sends a WhatsApp message instead of calling back.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The WhatsApp Business API integration is especially powerful for international sales. In markets like Latin America, India, and parts of Europe, WhatsApp is the primary communication channel. Meeting prospects there — with full conversation history and CRM sync — puts you ahead of competitors who only offer phone and email.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Set business hours for each channel independently. You might staff live chat from 9-5 but let WhatsApp messages queue overnight and get addressed first thing in the morning.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Who Is CallHippo Ideal For?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CallHippo is built for teams that treat the phone as a revenue driver, not just a support tool. Here is who gets the most value:",
